H0.text: What dog breed has Queen Elizabeth II traditionally had as pets. Poodle

H1.text: What dog breed has Queen Elizabeth II traditionally had as pets. Beagle

H2.text: What dog breed has Queen Elizabeth II traditionally had as pets. Afghan Hound

H3.text: What dog breed has Queen Elizabeth II traditionally had as pets. Corgi

A4.text: Queen Elizabeth II had a long association with Corgis, and she reportedly had said, 'my Corgis are family'.

A5.text: Queen Elizabeth II personally owned more than 30 Pembrokes or Corgi-Dachshund crosses, known as dorgis.
